P.S; DO TRY THE TAILSLIDE- A UNIQUE FEATURE TO THE MIG 29 AIR DISPLAY
ROUTINE.START FROM LEVEL FLIGHT AT 500KPH, PULL TO THE VERTICAL AND HOLD
IT.CLOSE THE THROTTLES AND WAIT UNTIL YOU SLIDE BACK. TO RECOVER, PULL THE
STICK BACK UNTIL THE NOSE STARTS TO COME DOWN,AT WHICH POINT YOU SHOULD APPLY
FULL POWER,RELAX THE STICK AND ACCELERATE AWAY.


