CODENAME: `REDWITCH`

A TERRORIST GROUP OPERATING WITHIN THE SOVIET TERRITORY HAVE BEEN DESTROYING
ROAD AND RAIL LINKS BETWEEN MAJOR CITIES.ONE OF THE REASONS THEY HAVE BEEN SO
HARD TO TRACK DOWN IS THAT THEY CONSTANTLY MOVE THEIR BASE,THUS MAKING IT
DIFFICULT TO PINPOINT THEIR LOCATION. IT IS ALSO BELIEVED THAT THEY ONLY TRAVEL
ON BACK ROADS AND ALWAYS AT NIGHT AT AVOID DETECTION.FORTUNATELY THE KGB HAVE
MANAGED TO INFILITRATE AN AGENT INTO THE TERRORIST GROUP,AND HE HAS GIVEN US A
DATE,TIME DATE AND APPROX POSITION OF THEIR CONVOY.YOUR MISSION IS TO PROVIDE
AIR SUPPORT FOR A SPETNATZ COMMANDO GROUP ACTING COVERTLY TO REMOVE THE
TERRORIST THREAT.

MISSION: TAKE OFF FROM AIRBASE,NAVIGATE TO PREDICTED AREA OF OPERATIONS, TRACK
TERRORIST VEHICLES TO BASE. DESTROY THE VEHICLES AND THE BASE..RETURN HOME.

